  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to glibmm</title>

    <para>The <application>glibmm</application> package is a set of C++ bindings
    for <application>Glib</application>.</para>

    &lfs70_built;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
